snippet.title: Amber Heard To Take Over Pirates Of The Caribbean From Johnny Depp?
snippet.description:
Amber Heard To Take Over Pirates Of The Caribbean From Johnny Depp? Watch this video till the end. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
_____________________________________________

PIRATES OF THE CARIBBEAN STAR Johnny Depp just lost his appeal against the latest UK court ruling in his "wife-beatr" case and now new reports claim that the Jack Sparrow actor's ex-wife Amber Heard is "in talks" with Margot Robbie to join Johnny's former franchise herself. We’ll tell you all you need to know about Amber Heard reportedly joining Pirates of the Caribbean franchise.
